-# The station screen — the exact pixels the Inky shows. Shared by /station (the clean
-# device view the shooter captures) and /station/preview (the framed e-ink emulation),
-# so the desktop preview can never drift from what the panel actually renders.
%main.screen.station
  %header.head
    %h1.wordmark Éist
    %p.place= Station.place&.dig(:en)
  %hr.rule/
  %section.collage-area{ "aria-label": "Birds heard today" }
    = render partial: 'panel'
  - if @news
    %p.news= @news
  - else
    %p.news.quiet ag éisteacht…
  %footer.foot
    %span= Time.current.strftime('%-l:%M %P')
    %span.moon #{@moon.emoji} #{@moon.name}
    %span= "#{@species_today} species"
